name: A Pink Depth III
description:
This piece is part of a series of mine (Under the Sea, 2017).

-

"There's something special about the pink depths of the ocean, where the light dances and swirls around like a pink liquid sky."

-

Abstract light-painting created with steel wool on fire in pitch darkness. It was complemented by digital art.

*

'A Pink Depth III', 2022
